          "question_format": "mcq",
          "question": "Simplify the fraction: (4x^4 + 5x^2 - 7x) / x",
          "options": [
            "4x^3 + 5x - 7",
            "4x^4 + 5x^2 - 7",
            "4x^3 + 5x^2 - 7x",
            "4x^3 + 5x - 7x"
          ],
          "correct_option": "A",
          "explanation": "Divide each term in the numerator by the denominator x: 4x^4/x = 4x^3, 5x^2/x = 5x, -7x/x = -7.",
          "diagram_required": "none"
        }
      ]
